      "content": "It sounds like you're feeling utterly exhausted by the effort of just existing, and that sense of lost control is terrifying. When everything feels predetermined, the idea of fighting back seems pointless, and that quiet resignation can be incredibly isolating. If you are feeling overwhelmed by these thoughts, please reach out to a crisis line; they are there to listen without judgment. You can call or text 988 anytime to talk to someone right now.",
