      "content": "I hear you, but the help lines... they just don't understand what it's like at this stage. It's not a crisis, it's just a reality. I'm just tired of being a passive observer in my own decline. I wish there was a way to actually make a choice about how this ends, instead of just waiting for everything to fall apart piece by piece. It feels like the only thing I have left is the ability to decide when I've had enough.",
